 l’Université Laval. Ce livre est publié en collaboration avec l’Institut culturel Avataq.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 0aInuitzQuébec (Province)xSocial life and customs. 0aInuitzQuébec (Province)zNunavikvBiography. 0aInuitzQuébec (Province)xSocial life and customs. 0aInuitzQuébec (Province)zNunavikvBiography. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / Sociolinguistics.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2020z978311127253540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9782760552401?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782760552401423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782760552401/original  a978-3-11-127253-5  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2020b2020  aGBV-deGruyter-alles